  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>I Am Busy Digging a Hole</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>– and you'll be busy too!</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3639230/extras/2979f4aab803c34d181035647cdce8e5.poster.avif?t=1755249863\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3639230/extras/2979f4aab803c34d181035647cdce8e5.webm?t=1755249863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3639230/extras/2979f4aab803c34d181035647cdce8e5.mp4?t=1755249863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Grab your shovel and discover what treasures lie beneath the surface</strong> in this delightful digging adventure. The deeper you go, the more exciting your journey becomes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3639230/extras/8c5f20a84a162a60f35d16dbfeb02a59.poster.avif?t=1755249863\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3639230/extras/8c5f20a84a162a60f35d16dbfeb02a59.webm?t=1755249863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3639230/extras/8c5f20a84a162a60f35d16dbfeb02a59.mp4?t=1755249863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dig through layers of earth to find valuable ores that you can sell for upgrades. Make your shovel stronger and your backpack bigger as you continue your busy digging life. Along the way, uncover rare dragons and ancient coins hiding in the dirt.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each dragon you rescue finds a home in your yard, creating a lively community above ground. And for those who dig deep enough, rumors of a mysterious cave dweller might lead to undiscovered worlds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3639230/extras/47e7c5c5175d40ba0fbb0434df292ae5.poster.avif?t=1755249863\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3639230/extras/47e7c5c5175d40ba0fbb0434df292ae5.webm?t=1755249863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3639230/extras/47e7c5c5175d40ba0fbb0434df292ae5.mp4?t=1755249863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Colorful Underground</strong> – Explore a vibrant world beneath your feet with surprises at every depth.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rewarding Progression</strong> – Sell ore, upgrade equipment, and watch your digging skills improve.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dragon Collection</strong> – Build a unique dragon sanctuary in your yard with each new discovery.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hidden Mysteries</strong> – Some secrets are buried deeper than others, waiting for the most determined diggers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Relaxing Experience</strong> – Get busy digging at your own pace in this charming underground adventure.</p></li></ul>",
